{"tid":1188393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳鍵鋒: 不評論《逃犯條例》, 答乜都死","createTime":"2019-06-06T08:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T10:25:13.000Z","uid":134071,"like":243,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"8ef4b4248a0cd8c3830ac2f8bfa049978c6f5262","tid":1188393,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:31:45.000Z","msg":"其實好難怪佢. &nbsp;無謂迫人. &nbsp;(起碼佢無幫中共)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190606/59684125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190606%2F59684125&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BgrktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=38018dcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190606%2F59684125&h=040100f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190606/59684125</a><br />\n<br />\n 2019年06月06日<br />\n【下星期大陸拍戲】唔評論《逃犯條例》大遊行 陳鍵鋒：答乜都死 <br />\n<br />\n陳鍵鋒將會下星期到內地拍攝網絡電影，今日在商台接受訪問時，表示已報讀神學遙距課程，預計修讀4年，他指等埋位時也會把握時間溫書和做功課。<br />\n<br />\n本身是基督徒的他，除了滿足父親想他讀一個學位的願望，亦表示是應天父的呼召：「我覺得可以停下來，諗啲新方向，想開多個新嘅視野，認識多啲。」他表示未來方向未必是要做牧師，牧師只是職銜，可能將來有機會把自己認識的和自己經歷跟別人分享。忠於宗教的他，一直以來接拍的角色不會大奸大惡，也不會接觸鬼神，這次拍網絡電影做二郎神，他表示是一個民間故事：「接角色會諗會唔會影響到其他人。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，被問會否呼應參與6月9日反對修訂《逃犯條例》大遊行，他說：「點解要講政治，呢啲話題答乜都死，梗係唔答啦。」身旁的經理人表示當日他不在港。"},{"pid":"9fb96a830fb38403fef762af806ddc734369af75","tid":1188393,"uid":35580,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3fb487c805043222294604ab41c71db6c8fc37","tid":1188393,"uid":148987,"like":186,"dislike":9,"score":177,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:33:18.000Z","msg":"可惜係中共邏輯咁樣答就當你反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137e64f355529aa7dcff380103f132b4d204664a","tid":1188393,"uid":81698,"like":91,"dislike":14,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:34:10.000Z","msg":"唔表態，罷睇！"},{"pid":"f2106470943280c08b82b6ad01319e1f54a67422","tid":1188393,"uid":55960,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:34:43.000Z","msg":"蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e50c20f14e22f2eb6a6041024dfcdc532f50f70","tid":1188393,"uid":53687,"like":148,"dislike":17,"score":131,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:34:45.000Z","msg":"陳鍵鋒作為公眾人士竟然唔表態，連登仔係時候批鬥了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faaf6bd9af027fb0b43556a4f90f78dd8ad5f548","tid":1188393,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:35:04.000Z","msg":"「接角色會諗會唔會影響到其他人。」<br />\n佢應該要同羅蘭姐學野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f3175cb8e18114740d5ee5db1905ac634ac0ac","tid":1188393,"uid":26333,"like":113,"dislike":2,"score":111,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:35:21.000Z","msg":"其實佢都講得岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6683447e6e58a40b8100be82bd0a3c76aea56c1","tid":1188393,"uid":48259,"like":155,"dislike":5,"score":150,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:38:01.000Z","msg":"都唔知幾時開始藝人要咁驚講政治"},{"pid":"85c43a0fd4ba26d081b9b24d37c1d86675f71ab5","tid":1188393,"uid":194298,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:39:23.000Z","msg":"基督徒？習帝有比你信基督咩"},{"pid":"cf40507a75b565ca24c4db74e343407fc574c83f","tid":1188393,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:41:53.000Z","msg":"遲下得閒搵陳牧師傾吓計先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ac43cad967aeb93f58562caa2ddeee71f78a34","tid":1188393,"uid":204533,"like":30,"dislike":4,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">陳鍵鋒將會下星期到內地拍攝網絡電影</span></strong>"},{"pid":"726fe10e0bf32cfe09d984906182859ebf3159bf","ti